snippet.title: SpaceKraft! Now Available on Steam
snippet.description:
SpaceKraft is out!
 👉Buy Now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1703020/SpaceKraft/?utm_source=reddit&utm_medium=trailer&utm_campaign=release

Explore planets, gather resources and craft systems with this physics based space simulation arcade game. Refuel, repair and upgrade your ship to find your way back to mother earth.

#trailer #spacesim #indiegame #gamedev #steam
